                    <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-pulse-purple to-pulse-cyan mb-4 pb-1 leading-normal">
                        Why This Changes Everything
                    </h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-pulse-cyan rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                            <span><strong class="text-white">Phase-Accurate Processing:</strong> All stems sum perfectly back to the original track</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-pulse-cyan rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                            <span><strong class="text-white">Multi-Model Cascade:</strong> Each component processed by specialized custom AI networks</span>
                        </li>
