                In your free analysis session, you'll see our Pulse Cascade Splitter™ break down your track and a professional reference in real-time. <strong class="text-pulse-cyan">The difference will be immediately obvious.</strong>
            </p>
            <a href="#offer-section" class="btn-lg shadow-cta-glow inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                See It In Action
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
                </svg>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .splitter-container {
        perspective: 1000px;
    }

    .splitter-image-wrapper {
        position: relative;
        transform-style: preserve-3d;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .splitter-image-wrapper:hover {
        transform: rotateY(-5deg) rotateX(2deg) translateZ(20px);
    }

    .splitter-image {
        transform: rotateY(-8deg) rotateX(4deg);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
    }

    .splitter-image:hover {
        transform: rotateY(-12deg) rotateX(6deg);
        box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }

    .splitter-reflection {
        position: absolute;
        top: 100%;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 50%;
        background: linear-gradient(
            to bottom,
            rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.3) 0%,
            rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.1) 50%,
            transparent 100%
        );
        transform: rotateY(-8deg) rotateX(4deg) scaleY(-1);
        transform-origin: top;
        opacity: 0.6;
        filter: blur(1px);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .splitter-image-wrapper:hover .splitter-reflection {
        transform: rotateY(-12deg) rotateX(6deg) scaleY(-1);
        opacity: 0.8;
    }

    /* Scroll animation */
    @keyframes float {
        0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
        50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
    }

    .splitter-container:hover {
        animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    /* Responsive adjustments */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .splitter-image {
            transform: rotateY(-4deg) rotateX(2deg);
        }
        
        .splitter-image:hover {
            transform: rotateY(-6deg) rotateX(3deg);
        }
        
        .splitter-reflection {
            transform: rotateY(-4deg) rotateX(2deg) scaleY(-1);
        }
        
        .splitter-image-wrapper:hover .splitter-reflection {
            transform: rotateY(-6deg) rotateX(3deg) scaleY(-1);
        }
    }
</style> 